title: 201 - The Pod Live From LA
description: Todays episode of The Pod weve got a full barn live from Los Angeles on cite here for Super Bowl XVI! After a failed group video attempt we had to battle through adversity to still give you guys an AMAZING show for the week! I hope you all enjoy!
